{% comment %}
  Mellow Premium Positioning Reminder
  Internal strategy section for premium pricing and brand positioning.
{% endcomment %}

<section id="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }}" class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder" aria-labelledby="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-heading-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__inner">
    <header class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__hero">
      <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__admin-label">Internal strategy reminder — not customer-facing</div>

      <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__eyebrow">
        {{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'Internal brand strategy' }}
      </p>

      <h2 id="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-heading-{{ section.id }}" class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__heading">
        {{ section.settings.heading | default: 'Premium positioning reminder for Mellow.' }}
      </h2>

      <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__subheading">
        {{ section.settings.subheading | default: 'A working strategy page for keeping the reflux routine, premium pricing, and product-format story clear while building the site.' }}
      </p>

      {% if section.settings.note != blank %}
        <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__note">{{ section.settings.note }}</p>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__intro-card">
        <p>To get people to pay a premium price, Mellow has to feel like the modern reflux solution, not just a nicer antacid.</p>
        <p>The premium cannot come from “prettier packaging” alone. It has to come from format, ritual, science, and relief moment ownership.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__grid mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__grid--wide-first">
      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__section-kicker">Strategy anchor</span>
        <h3>The premium-price argument</h3>
        <p>People will pay more when they believe Mellow is:</p>
        <ul class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__check-list">
          <li>more convenient than liquids</li>
          <li>more pleasant than chalky tablets</li>
          <li>more immediate-feeling than pills</li>
          <li>more modern than old pharmacy brands</li>
          <li>more purpose-built than generic antacids</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Your core premium claim is not “we taste better.”</p>
        <p>It is:</p>
        <blockquote class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pullquote">
          “Mellow gets there first. A single-serve raft-forming gel made for the moments reflux usually ruins.”
        </blockquote>
        <p>That makes the pouch format feel necessary, not decorative.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--accent">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">01</span>
        <h3>Sell the moment, not the ingredient</h3>
        <p>People do not pay premium for sodium alginate. They pay to save:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>dinner</li>
          <li>sleep</li>
          <li>travel</li>
          <li>work focus</li>
          <li>a date night</li>
          <li>a good meal</li>
          <li>feeling normal after eating</li>
        </ul>
        <p>So the site and ads should lead with stolen moments:</p>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__quote-stack" aria-label="Moment copy examples">
          <p>“Dinner was good. The night should be too.”</p>
          <p>“For the burn that shows up after the meal.”</p>
          <p>“After meals. Before bed. Back to you.”</p>
        </div>
        <p>That creates emotional value before you ask for money.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--table">
      <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">02</span>
      <h3>Make the single-serve pouch feel like the upgrade</h3>
      <p>The pouch is the biggest price-justifier. Lean into it hard.</p>

      <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__split-notes">
        <div>
          <h4>Old category:</h4>
          <p>chalky tablets, messy liquids, medicine cabinet bottles</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Mellow:</h4>
          <p>smooth gel pouch, pre-measured, portable, ritual-friendly</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Use comparison language:</p>
      <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__table-wrap" role="region" aria-label="Old reflux relief versus Mellow comparison" tabindex="0">
        <table class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__comparison-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">Old reflux relief</th>
              <th scope="col">Mellow</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="Old reflux relief">Chalky tablets</td>
              <td data-label="Mellow">Smooth gel</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="Old reflux relief">Big bottle</td>
              <td data-label="Mellow">Single-serve pouch</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="Old reflux relief">Reactive</td>
              <td data-label="Mellow">Taken after meals / before bed</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="Old reflux relief">Medicine-cabinet energy</td>
              <td data-label="Mellow">On-the-go daily routine</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="Old reflux relief">Generic antacid</td>
              <td data-label="Mellow">Raft-forming barrier approach</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>The premium is: better experience + better format + more modern mechanism.</p>
    </article>

    <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__grid">
      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">03</span>
        <h3>Do not over-discount the hero SKU</h3>
        <p>If you launch too cheap, you train people to see it as a commodity.</p>
        <p>Think in tiers:</p>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__tier-list">
          <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__tier">
            <strong>Trial pack: low-friction intro</strong>
            <span>Maybe 7–10 pouches around $12–18</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__tier">
            <strong>Core box: premium but not insane</strong>
            <span>20–30 pouches around $29–44, depending on COGS and positioning</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__tier">
            <strong>Subscribe &amp; save: makes premium feel rational</strong>
            <span>“Less than $1.50 per reflux moment” or similar, depending on real pricing.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Do not position it as “expensive antacid.” Position it as:</p>
        <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__emphasis-line">a daily reflux routine in single-serve pouches.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">04</span>
        <h3>Make the retail title do the hard clarity work</h3>
        <p>The front pack can say:</p>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pack-copy">
          <span>Reflux Calm</span>
          <span>Heartburn &amp; reflux relief</span>
        </div>
        <p>But the product listing should be more explicit:</p>
        <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__commerce-title">Mellow Reflux Calm Heartburn &amp; Reflux Relief Gel Pouches — Salted Caramel — 30ct</p>
        <p>That lets the packaging stay premium and simple while the commerce title handles search, category clarity, and value.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">05</span>
        <h3>Add a box/carton for premium value</h3>
        <p>A single pouch looks premium, but also risks looking small. For premium pricing, the consumer needs to instantly understand they are buying a system.</p>
        <p>Show:</p>
        <p class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__emphasis-line">30 single-serve pouches in a beautiful carton</p>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__anchor-lines">
          <p>The pouch is the daily object.</p>
          <p>The box is the value anchor.</p>
        </div>
        <p>This makes the price feel more justified because it looks like a real regimen, not a one-off sachet.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--science">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">06</span>
        <h3>Own “raft-forming” as the differentiator, but do not bury people in science</h3>
        <p>Front of pack can stay simple.</p>
        <p>Back of pack/site should make the premium logic obvious:</p>
        <blockquote class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__mini-quote">
          “Most antacids neutralize acid after it’s already there. Mellow forms a floating raft barrier designed to help keep reflux down.”
        </blockquote>
        <p>That is the “why it costs more” story.</p>
        <h4>Science hierarchy:</h4>
        <ol class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__process-list">
          <li><span>Simple front:</span> Soothe / Protect / Fast</li>
          <li><span>Back of pack:</span> raft explanation</li>
          <li><span>Website:</span> animation + studies + mechanism</li>
          <li><span>Ads:</span> before/after moment relief</li>
        </ol>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">07</span>
        <h3>Create premium proof signals</h3>
        <p>Premium buyers need confidence. Add trust without making it feel pharma.</p>
        <p>Strong signals:</p>
        <ul class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__check-list">
          <li>Doctor reviewed</li>
          <li>Built on alginate raft technology</li>
          <li>Non-chalky gel pouch</li>
          <li>Single-serve dosing</li>
          <li>After meals / before bed</li>
          <li>No giant bottle. No chalky chew.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Avoid making the pack too claim-heavy. Put the heavier proof on the PDP and landing page.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--flavor">
        <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">08</span>
        <h3>Make flavor part of the premium</h3>
        <p>Salted Caramel is actually a strong move because it makes the product feel indulgent and adult. But be careful: it should feel like a smooth functional gel, not candy.</p>
        <p>Language:</p>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__flavor-tags" aria-label="Flavor language">
          <span>Salted Caramel</span>
          <span>Smooth gel pouch</span>
          <span>Naturally flavored</span>
        </div>
        <p>Website copy:</p>
        <blockquote class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pullquote mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pullquote--small">
          “Relief should not taste like punishment.”
        </blockquote>
        <p>That line alone justifies premium against chalky antacids.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--bundles">
      <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">09</span>
      <h3>Use premium bundles</h3>
      <p>Instead of only selling a single box, sell routines:</p>
      <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__bundle-grid">
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__bundle"><strong>Dinner Kit</strong><span>30 pouches for after meals</span></div>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__bundle"><strong>Night Kit</strong><span>30 pouches for before bed</span></div>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__bundle"><strong>Full Routine</strong><span>60 pouches, best value</span></div>
        <div class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__bundle"><strong>Travel Pack</strong><span>10 pouches for bags, flights, work, restaurants</span></div>
      </div>
      <p>This reframes the price around use cases, not unit cost.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line">
      <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number">10</span>
      <h3>The premium positioning line</h3>
      <p>The cleanest strategic sentence is:</p>
      <blockquote class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pullquote mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__pullquote--hero">
        “Mellow is reflux relief redesigned for real life: a smooth, single-serve raft-forming gel pouch for after meals and before bed.”
      </blockquote>
      <p>That sentence justifies the price because it explains the entire upgrade.</p>
    </article>

    <footer class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card">
      <span class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__section-kicker">My recommendation</span>
      <h3>Build the modern reflux routine.</h3>
      <p>Do not try to be the cheapest reflux product. Try to be the first one people are proud to keep in their bag, on their nightstand, or in their kitchen drawer.</p>
      <p>The premium comes from this stack:</p>
      <ul class="mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__stack-list">
        <li>modern format</li>
        <li>better daily experience</li>
        <li>clear raft mechanism</li>
        <li>beautiful flavor system</li>
        <li>moment-based emotional copy</li>
        <li>regimen/carton value</li>
      </ul>
      <p>That is how Mellow becomes not “expensive antacid,” but the modern reflux routine.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} {
    --mpr-forest: #1A2D10;
    --mpr-ivory: #F0EBE0;
    --mpr-ivory-soft: #FBF7EF;
    --mpr-accent: #D04A2A;
    --mpr-blue: #3D6B8C;
    --mpr-caramel: #B8793A;
    --mpr-gold: #C79B52;
    --mpr-ink: #24311D;
    --mpr-muted: rgba(26, 45, 16, 0.72);
    --mpr-line: rgba(26, 45, 16, 0.16);
    --mpr-line-strong: rgba(26, 45, 16, 0.28);
    --mpr-card: rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.86);
    --mpr-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(26, 45, 16, 0.10);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(208, 74, 42, 0.12), transparent 34rem),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--mpr-ivory-soft) 0%, var(--mpr-ivory) 100%);
    color: var(--mpr-ink);
    font-family: inherit;
    padding: clamp(48px, 7vw, 96px) 18px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} *,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} *::before,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__inner {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1180px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);
    max-width: 920px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__admin-label,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__eyebrow,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__section-kicker,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number {
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__admin-label {
    background: var(--mpr-forest);
    color: var(--mpr-ivory);
    padding: 9px 12px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__eyebrow,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__section-kicker {
    color: var(--mpr-accent);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__number {
    background: rgba(208, 74, 42, 0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(208, 74, 42, 0.22);
    color: var(--mpr-accent);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding: 9px 11px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} h2,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} h3,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} h4,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} p,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} ul,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} ol,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} blockquote {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__heading {
    color: var(--mpr-forest);
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 86px);
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    line-height: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__subheading {
    color: var(--mpr-muted);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.4vw, 25px);
    line-height: 1.42;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__note {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--mpr-accent);
    color: var(--mpr-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-left: 14px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__intro-card,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card {
    background: var(--mpr-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--mpr-line);
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--mpr-shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__intro-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: clamp(22px, 3vw, 34px);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__intro-card p,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card p,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line p,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card p {
    color: var(--mpr-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.68;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__intro-card p:last-child,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card p:last-child,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line p:last-child,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__grid--wide-first {
    align-items: stretch;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.14fr) minmax(0, 0.86fr);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card {
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 38px);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--mpr-forest), #263B1B);
    color: var(--mpr-ivory);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature p,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature li {
    color: rgba(240, 235, 224, 0.82);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--accent {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(208, 74, 42, 0.12), rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.90));
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--science {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(61, 107, 140, 0.12), rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.90));
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--flavor {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(184, 121, 58, 0.14), rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.90));
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--table,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--bundles,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__positioning-line,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__final-card {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} h3 {
    color: var(--mpr-forest);
    font-size: clamp(25px, 3.2vw, 42px);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature h3,
  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__card--feature .mellow-premium-positioning-reminder__section-kicker {
    color: var(--mpr-ivory);
  }

  #mellow-premium-positioning-reminder-{{ section.id }} h4 {
    color: var(--mpr-forest);
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 1.2;
